summary: ...IVO LIKELY TO BECOME A REMNANT LOW LATER TODAY... As of 2:00 AM PDT Mon Aug 11 the center of Ivo was located near 22.7, -118.7 with movement WNW at 10 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1007 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
